 <trk>
  <name>Too hungover for this genuinely almost yacked all the ranch water up. Wanted to cry multiple times during this run but was so dehydrated that tears wouldn’t fall out. Words cannot describe the mix of disgust and euphoria I feel rn. Aggies beat the micks i</name>
